    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, get-it-done vehicle that won't break the bank? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, making it a solid choice for budget-conscious buyers who need reliable transportation. We want to be upfront: it shows its age with some visible wear, minor cosmetic imperfections, and the kind of character that comes with years on the road. What it lacks in polish it makes up for in value \u2014 a practical, honest buy for the right driver!",
      "price": 18000.0,
