    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, dependable ride that won't break the bank? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, making it a great option for everyday commuting and getting around town. You'll notice some cosmetic wear consistent with normal use, and while it's not showroom-perfect, it delivers honest, dependable transportation at a great value. If you're after a practical, no-fuss vehicle that gets you where you need to go, this one deserves a look!",
      "price": 17000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a good-condition car, offering reliable and practical used transportation for the discerning buyer. The exterior presents well overall, with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use \u2014 no significant dents, rust, or structural damage to report. The interior is clean and functional, with seating that shows moderate wear but remains comfortable, and all major controls and features working as intended. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has been maintained adequately; buyers can expect a solid, dependable drive without major surprises. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable & Ready to Go \u2013 A Genuine Good-Condition Find! \ud83d\ude97\n\nThis vehicle has been well looked after and it shows! You'll find it drives smoothly and handles everyday tasks with ease \u2014 whether that's the morning commute, errands around town, or a road trip getaway. It has normal wear consistent with its age, but nothing that gets in the way of dependable performance. The interior is clean and comfortable, and the mechanicals are in solid shape. No hidden surprises here \u2014 just an honest, well-maintained car at a fair price. If you're looking for reliable transportation without paying mint-condition prices, this one deserves a serious look! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, representing a solid, dependable choice for buyers seeking quality without the premium of a mint-condition car. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains good color and shine, though you'll notice a few minor scratches and light blemishes consistent with normal everyday use. There are no major dents or rust concerns. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery that shows modest wear on the high-contact areas like the driver's seat and door panels, but nothing that detracts significantly from the overall feel. Mechanically, this car has been properly maintained \u2014 it starts reliably, drives smoothly, and all major systems are functioning as expected. You can expect a vehicle that will serve you well day-to-day without the worries of a heavily worn car. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely transparent with you about what you're getting. The exterior shows significant deterioration \u2014 expect heavy scratching, multiple dents, and paint that is faded or peeling in several areas. The body panels may show rust or corrosion, and the overall appearance reflects years of hard use. Mechanically, this car requires attention: you should anticipate the need for repairs, and some systems may not be functioning reliably. The interior is worn throughout, with damaged upholstery, cracked or broken trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the associated risks and repair costs. We are pricing this honestly to reflect its true state.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
